message: Bob, I have a product that I believe would be of great value to you. It's something I've poured my heart and soul into, and I know it has the potential to be a real game-changer for your business.  I'm offering it to you for $1150000.  This price reflects its true worth, while still leaving room for you to profit handsomely. Let's discuss this further and see if we can make this happen.
